"Hello, friend! arguments: (\"a\" \"b\" \"c\")\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: deftp
#: doc/guix.texi:25220
msgid "This, as you can see, is a fairly sophisticated way to say hello.  @xref{Service Convenience,,, shepherd, The GNU Shepherd Manual}, for more info on actions."
